These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: card-games, collecting
Color: black, turquise
1. Color:black is in an even position##4
2. Color:turquise == Hobby:collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| Color     | turquise    | black   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Pet: goldfish, guinea-pig
Sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. Sport:sailing is in an odd position##4
2. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left of Pet:goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | goldfish        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
